    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i had a small cyst removed by my doctor like 3 days ago and the cut looks a bit weird today. its kind of red and warm to the touch and there is some yellow stuff oozing out a little bit. is that normal or should i be worried? i dont really wanna make a trip back to the clinic if i dont have to",
